data.description: Nice Price Adjustment on this very well maintained 2 bedroom, 1.5 Bath Single level Twin Home with direct access to garage. Lots of nice updates including all new Anderson Windows, Shutters, Water Heater & HVAC system. HOA replaced roof 3 years ago. Owned RO and water softener. Porcelain wood plank flooring in main living areas. 2nd bedroom has been extended and has own access to covered patio. Perfect for Lock and Leave. Super low maintenance complex. and close to so much. Peoria Sports complex, shopping restaurants, golf, medical facilities, the 101 freeway.
